OpenVAS is an open-source vulnerability scanner similar to commercial alternatives like Tenable Nessus, Qualys, and others. 

Thier website - https://www.openvas.org/ - provides a lot of great information on the platform. This document will cover the following:

Excellent install guide - https://hedgehogsecurity.co.uk/blog/2020/10/07/installing-openvas/ (Oct 2020)

* Single Node Deployment
* Multiple Node Deployment
* Scan tuning
* Updates & system management
* Scanning strategies for different networks.

